summary: NAR 01/21/2003. WHEN THE CONSUMER PULLED OVER TO REACH FOR AN ITEM, THE POWER SEAT WENT FORWARD AND BECAME BURIED IN THE CONSUMER ABDOMEN. THE CONSUMER HAD TO BE EXTRACATED FROM THE VEHICLE HE WAS REVIVED AND TAKEN TO THE HOSPITAL WHERE HE WAS IN INTENSIVE CARE, HOWEVER 2 DAYS LATER THE CONSUMER DIED FROM BRAIN DUE TO LACK OF OXYGEN. *JB
